item.title: Black Enchantress
item.description:
æ‰“åŒ…ä¸‹è½½ğŸ“¦ä»åœ¨å·¥äº‹ä¸­

Black Enchantress

As you’ll soon discover, Andrea Avery-Crusoe is not your typical comic book heroine. She’s amoral. She lacks a strong sense of personal responsibility. She’s not all that interested in helping people who need her help. Truth to tell, she’s a villain who enjoys making life miserable for anyone who gets in her way. So why did Heroic tape the Black Enchantress to star in our first new companion title to FLARE? Because we think, one you meet her, you’re going to fall in love.

item.title: Eternity Smith
item.description:
æ‰“åŒ…ä¸‹è½½ğŸ“¦ä»åœ¨å·¥äº‹ä¸­

Eternity Smith

Collected for the first time in a single volume, enjoy the original six-part story arc that introduced the classic science fiction hero, ETERNITY SMITH!

These classic tales, by Dennis Mallonee, Rick Hoberg, Tim Burgard, and Jim Janes, feature the time-traveling hero as he teams up with his super-spy daughter, SKYLARK SMITH and her CREW, on a desperate mission back to the present day. His challenge: to alter the stream of time in order to prevent a horrific future in which mankind stands on the brink of annihilation by an army of thinking machines.
